condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Article IV; paragraph 4.01 (ii) | Description :The Prime Minister will endorse the Resettlement Policy Framework| Due Date :11-Oct-2011
Finance Agreement :Article IV; paragraph 4.01(i) | Description :The Recipient will adopt the Project Operations Manual | Due Date:11-Oct-2011
Finance Agreement :Schedule 2: Section V | Description :The internal audit consultant shall carry out training of internal auditorsin WSCs and Project Provinces | Due Date :11-Jan-2012

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2; Section I; Part B; paragraph 1 | Description :The Recipient will make Sub-Loans and Sub-Grants tofinance Sub-Projects in accordance with the eligibility criteria and proceduresacceptable to the Association | Due Date :16-Jan-2012

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2; Section I; Part B; paragraph 2 (d)(ii)(H) and paragraph 3 (a)(ii)(H) | Description :Commitment byprovincial implementing agencies to appoint internal auditors with qualifications and experience and under Terms of Referenceacceptable to the Recipient and the Association | Due Date :11-Oct-2011

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2; Section I; Part B; paragraph 2(d)(ii)(I) | Description :The Recipient will (a) enable the WSCs tomaintain annual working ratios of not more than 90%; (b) share the annual debt service with the companies | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2; Section I; Part B; paragraph 6 | Description: The Recipient will: (a) enable the entities to achievefull recovery of their operations & maintenance (O&M) expenses; (b) provide the Project Provinces with financial support as needed| Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2; Section I; Part D; paragraph 6 | Description :In Da Lat, for the Dan Kia dam (a) an entity assignedfor dam safety oversight, (b) dam safety review completed, (c) O&M plan prepared | Due Date :31-Dec-2011

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2; Section IV; Part B; paragraph 1 (b)(i) | Description :Sub-Loan Agreement or Implementation Agreementhas to be signed within 90 days after the Financing Agreement is signed | Due Date :11-Oct-2011

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2; Section IV; Part B; paragraph 1 (b)(ii)(A) | Description: Projected Environmental Fee (as per Decree67) and Wastewater Fee (Decree 88) should be approved by the province, using cost recovery principles | Due Date :11-Oct-2011
Finance Agreement :Schedule 2; Section IV; Part B; paragraph 1(b)(ii)(B) | Description: A Sanitation Company responsible for O&Mactivities is assigned | Due Date :11-Oct-2011
